[package]
name = "clack-common"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2024"
rust-version = "1.85.0"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"

[dependencies]
clap-sys = "0.5.0"
bitflags = "2.10.0"

[dev-dependencies]
static_assertions = "1.1.0"

[lints.rust]
unsafe-op-in-unsafe-fn = "allow"

[lints.clippy]
undocumented-unsafe-blocks = "deny"

[package]
name = "clack-extensions"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2024"
rust-version = "1.85.0"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"

[dependencies]
clap-sys = "0.5.0"
bitflags = "2.10.0"

[dependencies.clack-plugin]
optional = true
path = "./plugin"
version = "0.1.0"

[dependencies.clack-host]
optional = true
default-features = false
path = "./host"
version = "0.1.0"

[dependencies.clack-common]
path = "./common"
version = "0.1.0"

[dependencies.raw-window-handle_05]
optional = true
package = "raw-window-handle"
version = "0.5.2"

[dependencies.raw-window-handle_06]
optional = true
package = "raw-window-handle"
version = "0.6.0"

[dev-dependencies.clack-host]
features = ["clack-plugin"]
path = "./host"
version = "0.1.0"
default-features = false

[features]
all-extensions = ["audio-ports", "audio-ports-activation", "audio-ports-config", "clap-wrapper", "event-registry", "gui", "latency", "log", "note-name", "note-ports", "params", "param-indication", "posix-fd", "remote-controls", "render", "state", "state-context", "tail", "thread-check", "thread-pool", "timer", "track-info", "voice-info"]
audio-ports = []
audio-ports-activation = []
audio-ports-config = []
clap-wrapper = []
event-registry = []
gui = []
latency = []
log = []
note-name = []
note-ports = []
params = []
param-indication = []
posix-fd = []
remote-controls = []
render = []
state = []
state-context = ["state"]
tail = []
thread-check = []
thread-pool = []
timer = []
track-info = ["audio-ports"]
voice-info = []

[lints.rust]
unsafe-op-in-unsafe-fn = "allow"

[lints.clippy]
undocumented-unsafe-blocks = "deny"

[package]
name = "clack-host"
version = "0.1.0"
edition = "2024"
rust-version = "1.85.0"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"

[dependencies]
clap-sys = "0.5.0"

[dependencies.clack-common]
path = "./common"
version = "0.1.0"

[dependencies.clack-plugin]
optional = true
path = "./plugin"
version = "0.1.0"

[dependencies.libloading]
optional = true
version = "0.8.1"

[features]
default = ["libloading"]
libloading = ["dep:libloading"]
clack-plugin = ["dep:clack-plugin"]

[dev-dependencies]
static_assertions = "1.1.0"

[dev-dependencies.clack-plugin]
path = "./plugin"
version = "0.1.0"

[dev-dependencies.clack-extensions]
features = ["clack-host", "clack-plugin", "latency", "log", "state", "timer"]
path = "./extensions"
version = "0.1.0"

[lints.rust]
unsafe-op-in-unsafe-fn = "allow"

[lints.clippy]
undocumented-unsafe-blocks = "deny"

[package]
authors = ["Will Medrano <will.s.medrano@gmail.com", "Henna Haahti <grejppi@gmail.com>"]
build = "build.rs"
description = "Library for discovering and running LV2 plugins."
documentation = "https://docs.rs/lilv"
edition = "2024"
keywords = ["lilv", "lv2", "audio"]
license = "MIT"
name = "lilv"
readme = "README.md"
version = "0.2.5"

[dependencies]
lilv-sys = "0.2.2"
lv2_raw = "0.3"
parking_lot = "0.12.4"

[build-dependencies]
pkg-config = "0.3"

[patch.crates-io.lv2_raw]
git = "https://github.com/mlm-games/lv2_raw"

[patch.crates-io.lilv-sys]
git = "https://github.com/mlm-games/lilv-sys-rs"

[package]
name = "lilv-sys"
version = "0.2.2"
authors = ["Will Medrano <will.s.medrano@gmail.com>"]
description = "FFI for lilv, a C library to make the use of LV2 plugins simple"
edition = "2024"
license = "MIT"
keywords = ["audio", "lilv", "lv2"]
repository = "https://github.com/mlm-games/lilv-sys-rs"

[dependencies]
lv2_raw = "0.3"

[patch.crates-io.lv2_raw]
git = "https://github.com/mlm-games/lv2_raw"

[package]
authors = ["Will S. Medrano <will.s.medrano@gmail.com>"]
description = "livi is a library for hosting LV2 plugins."
documentation = "https://docs.rs/livi"
edition = "2024"
keywords = ["realtime", "audio", "lv2", "plugins", "music"]
license = "MIT"
name = "livi"
readme = "README.md"
repository = "https://github.com/wmedrano/livi-rs"
version = "0.8.0"

[dependencies]
hound = "3.5.1"
lilv = "0.2.5"
log = "0.4"
lv2_raw = "0.3.0"
ringbuf = "0.4.8"

[dev-dependencies]
env_logger = "0.11.8"
lazy_static = "1.4"
structopt = "0.3"
tempfile = "3.21.0"
lv2-sys = "2"

[dev-dependencies.jack]
version = "0.11"

[patch.crates-io.lilv]
git = "https://github.com/mlm-games/lilv-rs"
branch = "main"

[patch.crates-io.lv2_raw]
git = "https://github.com/mlm-games/lv2_raw"

[patch.crates-io.lilv-sys]
git = "https://github.com/mlm-games/lilv-sys-rs"
branch = "main"

[package]
name = "lv2_raw"
version = "0.3.0"
authors = ["ragebreaker", "poidl <hoitaus@gmail.com>"]
description = "Exposes the raw LV2 interface (C) to Rust. Also attempts to implement some idiomatic Rust concepts (e.g. iterators)."
documentation = "https://docs.rs/lv2_raw/0.2.0/lv2_raw/"
homepage = "https://github.com/mlm-games/lv2_raw"
repository = "https://github.com/mlm-games/lv2_raw"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = ["lv2", "audio", "plugin", "ffi"]
license = "ISC OR MIT OR Apache-2.0"
edition = "2024"

[dependencies]
libc = "0.2"

[workspace]
members = [".", "examples/browser"]

[package]
name = "midir"
version = "0.11.2"
authors = ["Patrick Reisert"]
description = "A cross-platform, realtime MIDI processing library, inspired by RtMidi."
repository = "https://github.com/Boddlnagg/midir"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = ["midi", "audio", "music", "sound"]
categories = ["multimedia::audio", "api-bindings"]
license = "MIT"
edition = "2021"

[features]
default = []
avoid_timestamping = []
coremidi_send_timestamped = []
jack = ["jack-sys", "libc"]
winrt = ["windows/Foundation", "windows/Foundation_Collections", "windows/Devices_Midi", "windows/Devices_Enumeration", "windows/Storage_Streams", "windows/Win32_System_WinRT"]

[dependencies]
bitflags = "1.2"

[dependencies.jack-sys]
version = "0.5"
optional = true

[dependencies.libc]
version = "0.2.21"
optional = true

[target."cfg(target_os = \"linux\")".dependencies]
alsa = "0.9.0"
libc = "0.2.21"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"ios\")".dependencies]
coremidi = "0.8.0"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"macos\")".dependencies]
coremidi = "0.8.0"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"windows\")".dependencies.windows]
version = "0.56"
features = ["Win32_Foundation", "Win32_Media", "Win32_Media_Multimedia", "Win32_Media_Audio"]

[target."cfg(target_os = \"windows\")".dependencies.parking_lot]
version = "0.12.1"

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies]
js-sys = "0.3"
wasm-bindgen = "0.2"

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dependencies.web-sys]
version = "0.3"
features = ["Event", "Navigator", "Window", "MidiAccess", "MidiInput", "MidiInputMap", "MidiMessageEvent", "MidiOptions", "MidiOutput", "MidiOutputMap", "MidiPort", "MidiPortType"]

[target."cfg(target_arch = \"wasm32\")".dev-dependencies]
wasm-bindgen-test = "0.2"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"android\")".dependencies]
ndk-context = "0.1"
jni-min-helper = "0.3"

[target."cfg(target_os = \"android\")".dependencies.jni]
version = "0.21"
default-features = false

[target."cfg(target_os = \"android\")".build-dependencies]
cc = "1.0"

[package]
name = "midly"
version = "0.5.3"
edition = "2024"
authors = ["negamartin"]
include = ["/src/*", "/Cargo.toml"]
description = "Fast MIDI decoder and encoder both for .mid files and real-time MIDI events"
repository = "https://github.com/negamartin/midly"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = ["midi", "no_std", "audio", "parser"]
categories = ["multimedia::audio", "multimedia::encoding", "multimedia"]
license = "Unlicense"

[features]
default = ["alloc", "std", "parallel", "serde"]
strict = []
serde = ["dep:serde", "dep:serde_bytes"]
alloc = []
std = ["alloc"]
parallel = ["std", "rayon"]

[dependencies.rayon]
version = "1"
optional = true

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1"
default-features = false
features = ["derive"]
optional = true

[dependencies.serde_bytes]
version = "0.11"
optional = true

[dev-dependencies]
serde_json = "1"

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/prokopyl/clack"]
git = "https://github.com/prokopyl/clack"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "main"

[source."https://github.com/mlm-games/lilv-rs"]
git = "https://github.com/mlm-games/lilv-rs"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "main"

[source."https://github.com/mlm-games/lilv-sys-rs"]
git = "https://github.com/mlm-games/lilv-sys-rs"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "main"

[source."https://github.com/mlm-games/livi-rs"]
git = "https://github.com/mlm-games/livi-rs"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
branch = "main"

[source."https://github.com/mlm-games/lv2_raw"]
git = "https://github.com/mlm-games/lv2_raw"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/mlm-games/midir"]
git = "https://github.com/mlm-games/midir"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
rev = "28e276a3731f2480bddac0b7813a4bab573037f8"

[source."https://github.com/mlm-games/midly"]
git = "https://github.com/mlm-games/midly"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
